      "created_at": "2018-01-25T22:14:03.057Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Imazhi i fundit i “Socialism” i Godard.<br>\nPikerisht mbi “vjedhjen” e filmave:<br>\nNë sfond, “FBI WARNING”.<br>\nMbi të (<strong>mbi të !!</strong>) : “Kur ligji nuk eshte i drejte, e drejta e tejkalon ligjin”<br>\n<img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/wink.png?v=6\" title=\":wink:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":wink:\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/8/8a34c574eb88cc60dbe84e52da66f50346f14680.png\" alt=\"image\" width=\"718\" height=\"406\"></p>",
