      "created_at": "2018-01-25T22:37:46.554Z",
      "cooked": "<p>“There’s no such thing as intellectual property, there’s only intellectual responsibility.”</p>\n<p>tha Godard me ate rast <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/nerd_face.png?v=5\" title=\":nerd_face:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":nerd_face:\"></p>",
